  <answer><![CDATA[<div class="c-page-content">
<p>Italy has some amazing resorts with beautiful landscapes to choose from - between <a data-udi="umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887}" title="Sauze d'Oulx">Sauze d'Oulx</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/f5a15898b6694ef6a1c755346a0e1ba8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f5a15898b6694ef6a1c755346a0e1ba8}" title="Corvara &amp; Colfosco">Corvara</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/090d2ea7dadc4d03ba25ba2f7aaac686" href="/{localLink:umb://document/090d2ea7dadc4d03ba25ba2f7aaac686}" title="Champoluc">Champoluc</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97}" title="Selva">Selva</a> - you are spoiled for choice. Plus, Corvara and Selva are in the UNESCO world heritage site of the <a data-udi="umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393" href="/{localLink:umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393}" title="The Dolomites Ski Area">Dolomites</a>, making them very popular choices.</p>
</div>]]></answer>
